    "date": "2022-02-08T14:26:13Z",
    "text": "Virtual Currency Tax Fairness Act of 2022\n\nThis bill excludes from gross income, for income tax purposes, up to $200 of gain from the disposition of virtual currency in a personal transaction. The bill defines virtual currency as a digital representation of value that is used as a medium of exchange and is not otherwise currency."
